PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FA knife attack on an innocent member
OL,7,Fof the public could have been
OL,8,Fprevented had a patient received
OL,9,Fbetter mental health care, an
OL,10,FOmbudsman has said.
OL,12,FThe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,13,FOmbudsman (PHSO) said that the 31-year-
OL,14,Fold man, who has since been diagnosed
OL,15,Fwith schizophrenia, received "poor
OL,16,Fmental health care" from Kent and
OL,17,FMedway NHS and Social Care Partnership
OL,18,FTrust, now called Kent and Medway
OL,19,FMental Health NHS Trust.
OL,26,@wD@^OUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FThe PHSO said there was a "series" of
OL,7,Ffailings by the trust in the 12 months
OL,8,Frunning up to the stabbing in November
OL,9,F2020.
OL,11,F"This is a sad case involving a
OL,12,Fvulnerable man who posed a risk not
OL,13,Fonly to himself but to others," said
OL,14,FRebecca Hilsenrath, chief executive
OL,15,Fofficer of PHSO.
OL,17,F"A risk that tragically became reality
OL,18,Fwhen he attacked an innocent member of
OL,19,Fthe public.
OL,26,@nD@[OUnD@bO]sD@AOUuD@_O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,F"It highlights the stark consequences
OL,7,Fof poor mental health care, not just
OL,8,Ffor patients, but also for their
OL,9,Ffamilies, carers and even strangers."
OL,11,FThe PHSO said the failings included
OL,12,Fpoor care planning and discharging the
OL,13,Fpatient without reviewing his risk
OL,14,Flevel.
OL,16,FIt said they might have contributed to
OL,17,Fthe man's mental health decline.
OL,19,FAnd had the man received safe and
OL,20,Fappropriate care, the stabbing might
OL,21,Fnot have occurred, the PHSO said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation after the patient's
OL,8,Fmother, a 57-year-old, complained
OL,9,Fabout the care her son received.
OL,11,FThe woman, who chose to remain
OL,12,Fanonymous, said her son began
OL,13,Fstruggling with symptoms of paranoia
OL,14,Fand anxiety in early 2019, and he was
OL,15,Fdetained by police and admitted to
OL,16,Fhospital in October.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FIn April and May 2020 the woman
OL,7,Frepeatedly contacted the mental health
OL,8,Fteam, reporting behaviour including
OL,9,Fher son ripping up blinds and carpets,
OL,10,Fplacing furniture in the garden and
OL,11,Fblocking her from leaving the house.
OL,13,FShe told staff she was "frightened"
OL,14,Fand had hidden in the car for hours,
OL,15,Fand she tried to get help.
OL,17,FThe PHSO said the trust knew the man
OL,18,Fwas in crisis but failed to develop a
OL,19,Fcare plan, and instead told her to
OL,20,Fcontact police ` falling short of
OL,21,Fnational guidelines.
OL,26,@uD@XOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FHe was later arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fcriminal damage and detained in
OL,8,Fhospital, but in June 2020 he was
OL,9,Freleased to the community.
OL,11,FBut in the three months that followed
OL,12,F` which was during the Covid-19
OL,13,Fpandemic ` the man received three
OL,14,Fphone calls but was not seen by the
OL,15,Fcare team in person.
OL,17,FHe was discharged from the trust's
OL,18,Fcare in October.
OL,20,FOne month later he stabbed a member of
OL,21,Fthe public ` a man in his 30s.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman found the failings left
OL,7,Fthe man's mother in distress for over
OL,8,Fa year and caused her to fear for her
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FThe mother said: "I was too scared to
OL,12,Fbe in my home, so I sat in my car for
OL,13,Fhours calling staff begging them to
OL,14,Fhelp.
OL,16,F"For months I was telling them he was
OL,17,Fin psychosis. I was terrified. They
OL,18,Foffered no real help.
OL,20,F"They failed my son, they failed me,
OL,21,Fand they failed the person he hurt.
OL,26,@sD@ROUxD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,F"Before he committed this crime, he
OL,7,Fhad never been violent. I have no
OL,8,Fdoubt that he hurt someone because of
OL,9,Fthe failings of the community mental
OL,10,Fhealth team."
OL,12,FMs Hilsenrath added: "The patient's
OL,13,Fmother repeatedly raised concerns
OL,14,Fabout her son's deteriorating
OL,15,Fcondition and the risks he posed.
OL,17,F"She was so fearful that she felt
OL,18,Fforced to hide in her car rather than
OL,19,Fremain in the home they shared.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]tD@VOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,F"Despite her repeated pleas for help,
OL,7,Fshe was badly let down by the trust
OL,8,Fand left to cope alone without the
OL,9,Fsupport she urgently needed.
OL,11,F"For over a year, she endured a
OL,12,Ffrightening and distressing situation.
OL,13,FDuring periods when her son was in
OL,14,Fcrisis, her requests for help went
OL,15,Flargely unanswered, leaving her in
OL,16,Ffear for her safety.
OL,18,F"There is still significant work to be
OL,19,Fdone to embed a culture within mental
OL,20,Fhealth services that learns from past
OL,21,Fmistakes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,F"While there have been some
OL,7,Fimprovements, including steps towards
OL,8,Freform of the Mental Health Act and
OL,9,Fongoing Government inquiries, these
OL,10,Fmust lead to real change on the ground
OL,11,F` change that improves services and
OL,12,Fkeeps people safe."
OL,14,FA Kent and Medway Mental Health NHS
OL,15,FTrust spokesperson said, "This was a
OL,16,Fdeeply serious and complex case, and
OL,17,Fwe recognise the distress experienced
OL,18,Fby the family.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@SO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777546977
OL,3,CKent man stabbed innocent victim after
OL,4,C'poor' mental health care
OL,6,F"Concerns raised in 2021 were fully
OL,7,Finvestigated, including through close
OL,8,Fengagement with the Parliamentary and
OL,9,FHealth Service Ombudsman, and we have
OL,10,Fbeen open and transparent throughout
OL,11,Fthat process.
OL,13,F"We apologise for where care and
OL,14,Fsupport did not meet expected
OL,15,Fstandards and have taken action to
OL,16,Fstrengthen community mental health
OL,17,Fservices in line with the National
OL,18,FCommunity Mental Health Framework."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
